HEADWORD: Metagraphy
<hw>Me*tag"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>meta-</ets> + <ets>-graphy</ets>.]</ety> <def>The art or act of
rendering the letters of the alphabet of one language into the possible
equivalents of another; transliteration.</def>
<rj><au>Stormonth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

